    46вҶ’## Contributing
    47вҶ’
    48вҶ’mdBook is free and open source. You can find the source code on
    49вҶ’[GitHub](https://github.com/rust-lang/mdBook) and issues and feature requests can be posted on
    50вҶ’the [GitHub issue tracker](https://github.com/rust-lang/mdBook/issues). mdBook relies on the community to fix bugs and
    51вҶ’add features: if you'd like to contribute, please read
