format/theme/index-hbs.md
     1вҶ’# index.hbs
     2вҶ’
     3вҶ’`index.hbs` is the handlebars template that is used to render the book. The
     4вҶ’markdown files are processed to html and then injected in that template.
     5вҶ’
     6вҶ’If you want to change the layout or style of your book, chances are that you
     7вҶ’will have to modify this template a little bit. Here is what you need to know.
      вҶ’вҖҰ
     9вҶ’## Data
    10вҶ’
    11вҶ’A lot of data is exposed to the handlebars template with the "context". In the
    12вҶ’handlebars template you can access this information by using
    13вҶ’
    14вҶ’```handlebars
    15вҶ’{{name_of_property}}
      вҶ’вҖҰ
    41вҶ’## Handlebars helpers
    42вҶ’
    43вҶ’In addition to the properties you can access, there are some handlebars helpers
    44вҶ’at your disposal.
    45вҶ’
    46вҶ’### toc
    47вҶ’
    48вҶ’The toc helper is used like this
    49вҶ’
    50вҶ’```handlebars
    51вҶ’{{#toc}}{{/toc}}
    52вҶ’```
      вҶ’вҖҰ
    80вҶ’### resource
    81вҶ’
    82вҶ’The path to a static file.
    83вҶ’It implicitly includes `path_to_root`,
    84вҶ’and accounts for files that are renamed with a hash in their filename.
    85вҶ’
    86вҶ’```handlebars
      вҶ’вҖҰ
    90вҶ’### fa
    91вҶ’
    92вҶ’mdBook includes a copy of [Font Awesome Free's](https://fontawesome.com)
    93вҶ’MIT-licensed SVG files. It accepts three positional arguments:
    94вҶ’
    95вҶ’1. Type: one of "solid", "regular", and "brands" (light and duotone are not
    96вҶ’   currently supported)
      вҶ’вҖҰ
format/theme/syntax-highlighting.md
     1вҶ’# Syntax highlighting
     2вҶ’
     3вҶ’mdBook uses [Highlight.js](https://highlightjs.org) with a custom theme
     4вҶ’for syntax highlighting.
     5вҶ’
     6вҶ’Automatic language detection has been turned off, so you will probably want to
     7вҶ’specify the programming language you use like this:
      вҶ’вҖҰ
    17вҶ’## Supported languages
    18вҶ’
    19вҶ’These languages are supported by default, but you can add more by supplying
    20вҶ’your own `highlight.js` file:
    21вҶ’
    22вҶ’- apache
    23вҶ’- armasm
      вҶ’вҖҰ
    68вҶ’## Custom theme
    69вҶ’Like the rest of the theme, the files used for syntax highlighting can be
    70вҶ’overridden with your own.
    71вҶ’
    72вҶ’- ***highlight.js*** normally you shouldn't have to overwrite this file, unless
    73вҶ’  you want to use a more recent version.
    74вҶ’- ***highlight.css*** theme used by highlight.js for syntax highlighting.
      вҶ’вҖҰ
    82вҶ’## Improve default theme
    83вҶ’
    84вҶ’If you think the default theme doesn't look quite right for a specific language,
    85вҶ’or could be improved, feel free to [submit a new
    86вҶ’issue](https://github.com/rust-lang/mdBook/issues) explaining what you
    87вҶ’have in mind and I will take a look at it.
    88вҶ’
      вҶ’вҖҰ
